  "texts": [
    "The INN encoding ensures that critical structural and compositional features are effectively captured, while the ENN encoding maintains rotational and translational invariance, which is essential for modeling the underlying physical symmetries of complex materials.",
    "This hierarchical and combinatorial approach enables the efficient simulation of Li diffusivity, paving the way for addressing largescale material complexities while ensuring computational efficiency and precision, thus advancing the design and optimization of next-generation solid-state conductors.",
    "Therefore, the development of robust encoding frameworks tailored to inorganic crystals and polymer materials, combined with the establishment of a comprehensive database, will not only enhance the accuracy and predictive power of ML models but also enable the discovery of novel solid-state electrolytes with optimized properties.",
    "This approach paves the way for accelerated materials design and innovation, overcoming the current limitations associated with data sparsity and feature complexity.",
    "The fast-charging capability can be addressed from two aspects, including optimizing charging protocols and developing new materials 96."
